    public static final class SourceContext.Builder
extends com.google.protobuf.GeneratedMessageV3.Builder<SourceContext.Builder>
implements SourceContextOrBuilder
     A SourceContext is a reference to a tree of files. A SourceContext together
 with a path point to a unique revision of a single file or directory.
    Protobuf type grafeas.v1beta1.source.SourceContext
